title: Senator Tammy Duckworth (D-IL), "Every Day Is a Gift"
description:
Senator Tammy Duckworth (D-IL) talks about her life and career in the military and in the U.S. Senate. She’s interviewed by Politico’s congressional editor Elana Schor. www.oracle.com/goto/cspan.
